 * date: 3th November 2021
 * ================================================================================================
 * Father process create two child process, one uses Bubble sort and the   
 * second uses Quick sort to sort array of size 50,000 repeating this 50 times. prints the results
 * of each child process to an output files and calculate the max,min and average runtime of each
 * sorting method. In addition the father calculate its runtime of its self.
 * ================================================================================================
 * Compile: gcc -Wall ex1a.c -o ex1
 * Run: ./ex1 input-file srand
 * Run time of father process: 469.592473
 ==================================================================================================
